    <abstract>
      <t>Dual-stack deployments require both IPv4 and IPv6 transfer capabilities are deployed in parallel. IPv6-only is considered as the ultimate stage where only IPv6 transfer capabilities are used while ensuring global reachability. This document specifies requirements when deploying IPv6-only in multi-domain networks.</t>
